   The Tubbo on the Sky Terrace

The Tubbo on the Sky Terrace

   The waiting's almost over. The Tubbo on the Sky Terrace will be back on
   November 1st! Enjoy cheese specialities, mulled wine and much more...

   Schweizerhof Bern

   The hotel offers 99 stylish rooms and suites, an 800m^2 conference
   center with a stunning ballroom, the Jack’s Brasserie restaurant and
   the sophisticated Lobby-Lounge-Bar, Cigar Lounge, a 500m^2wellness SPA
   and the elegant Sky Terrace with a 360° panorama view.

